BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 554 Td (Apple Watch offers comprehensive health and fitness tracking with excellent senior features.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 533 Td (Fitbit provides simple, affordable tracking with a long battery life.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 512 Td (Garmin excels at GPS tracking for walkers, hikers, and outdoor exercisers.) Tj ET
