BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 470 Td (WHOOP strap focuses on recovery and strain metrics for data-driven exercisers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 449 Td (Key features to prioritize: heart rate accuracy, fall detection, and ease of use.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 428 Td (Battery life matters - choose a device you will not forget to charge frequently.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 407 Td (Water resistance is important if you swim or prefer not removing it for showers.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 386 Td (Start with basic features and explore advanced ones as you become comfortable.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 365 Td (Any wearable is better than none - do not let perfect be the enemy of good.) Tj ET

