BT 0 g /F2 12 Tf 36 608 Td (Chapter 19: 12-Week AI Fitness Starter Plan) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 36 600 m 396 600 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 575 Td (Weeks 1-2: Walk 10-15 minutes daily with step tracker. Focus on building the habit.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 554 Td (Weeks 3-4: Add 5 minutes of gentle stretching after each walk. Try a flexibility app.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 533 Td (Weeks 5-6: Introduce 2 strength sessions per week \(bodyweight or light bands, 10 min each\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 512 Td (Weeks 7-8: Increase walks to 20-25 minutes. Add balance exercises 3 times per week.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 491 Td (Weeks 9-10: Try a virtual group fitness class once per week. Explore different formats.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 470 Td (Weeks 11-12: Build your full routine: walk daily, strength 2-3x, flexibility daily, balance 3x.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 449 Td (Listen to AI recovery recommendations - rest when your body says rest.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 428 Td (Track your improvements weekly: steps, strength, flexibility, and energy levels.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 407 Td (Adjust the timeline if needed - going slower is always better than getting injured.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 386 Td (By week 12, you will have a sustainable routine that AI continues to adapt and improve.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 9.8 Tf 36 365 Td (Celebrate completing 12 weeks - you have built a foundation for years of active aging.) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
